item.title: Help how to change home delta base
item.dc:creator: @Mybb Mybb
item.description:
@Mybb wrote:

to change your starting coords, and the coords you go to when you die, open up your Player.java and look for the starting coordinates. It will be something like toX = ####; toY = ####; Now to change your home teleport, you have to change that in your ClickingMost.java file look in that file for the text that displays the same text that appears when you “hover over” the home tele on your spellbook, and look for the corresponding coordinates near that text.
